\partial_{0}^{2}W_{i}^{a}+\partial_{k}W_{ik}^{a}+g\epsilon^{abc}W_{k}^{b}W_{ik}^{c}-g\text{Im }\left[\phi^{\dagger}\sigma^{a}\left(D_{i}\phi\right)\right]=0
